    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1872-12-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1872-12-24T00:00:00-05:00" n="63" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d63">
                <head>No. 369.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName corresp="#p_DES1" type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr. <persName corresp="#p_HF1" type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Received December 25, 10 a.m.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1872-12-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">24 <hi rend="italic">December</hi>, 1872</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Minister of ultramar presented to-day in the chambers of deputies the bill
                        for immediate emancipation in Porto Rico. No doubt is entertained of its
                        speedy passage.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_DES1">SICKLES</persName>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
